tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE InsuranceAgents (
    agent_id INT,
    agent_name VARCHAR(50),
    policy_id INT,
    policy_type VARCHAR(50),
    policy_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    commission_rate DECIMAL(5, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE commission_payments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    agent_id INT,
    policy_id INT,
    commission_amount DECIMAL,
    commission_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE agents (
    agent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE policies (
    policy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    policy_name VARCHAR(100),
    policy_type VARCHAR(50),
    policy_amount DECIMAL,
    start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE commissions (
    commission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    agent_id INT,
    policy_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    commission_amount DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (agent_id) REFERENCES agents(agent_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (policy_id) REFERENCES policies(policy_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Policies (
    policy_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    policy_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    policy_amount DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    agent_id INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (agent_id) REFERENCES InsuranceAgents(agent_id)
);

CREATE TABLE CommissionPayments (
    payment_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    policy_id INT NOT NULL,
    agent_id INT NOT NULL,
    payment_amount DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    payment_date DATE NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (policy_id) REFERENCES Policies(policy_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (agent_id) REFERENCES InsuranceAgents(agent_id)
);

CREATE TABLE CommissionTriggers (
    trigger_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    trigger_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trigger_definition TEXT NOT NULL,
    agent_id INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (agent_id) REFERENCES InsuranceAgents(agent_id)
);
